videos.description: Jalen Rose is impressed with LeBron James' performance against Giannis Antetokounmpo and the Bucks, while Paul Pierce is adamant Giannis needs more help in order for the Bucks to go far in the playoffs.

videos.headline: Did LeBron, Lakers send a message to Giannis and the Bucks?

videos.description: With the possibility looming that teams will have to play in empty arenas due to Coronavirus, LeBron James adamantly states he will not play in any games if the fans are not there.

videos.headline: LeBron: If the arenas are empty, I'm not playing

videos.description: Dave McMenamin highlights the pivotal moments from LeBron James leading his Lakers to a victory over Giannis Antetokounmpo and the Bucks on Friday night.
